---
title: Homemade Cheesy Beef & Halloumi Burger with Caramelised Onion Mayo & Kūmara Fries
description: Top tonight's perfectly seasoned beef patties and halloumi with melty Cheddar and sticky caramelised onion and you'll be sitting down to a dish that's a contender for the 'Best Burger Ever'.

